{"tid":56090,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"去完緬甸黎，你問我答","createTime":"2016-12-27T02:54:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-12T00:40:18.000Z","uid":60315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"654f111b24120fe262cff8a59e44315ec0fdedcb","tid":56090,"uid":60315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T02:54:22.000Z","msg":"今個聖誕去左仰光同曼德勒黎<br />\n其實緬甸唔係想像中咁落後<br />\n識答我都會盡量答<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1494d247caaacab37a8bf4815fdfbf8bb536fd80","tid":56090,"uid":13391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:10:42.000Z","msg":"我下個月都會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問下嗰邊錢面額咁大咁多 你會點袋<br />\n同埋你去係揹backpack定有帶喼<br />\n<br />\n我淨係去仰光蒲甘<br />\n想帶個細喼又怕唔方便"},{"pid":"279d5cb3e493fc7b73eca039d9f9f959407e4873","tid":56090,"uid":7223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:11:35.000Z","msg":"緬甸有咩係必食"},{"pid":"7e32d64ad256aebd3f8bef5195e97820f1b74721","tid":56090,"uid":45749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:12:00.000Z","msg":"我三月去， 果邊會唔會好亂？好似黃警緊"},{"pid":"db7e2dedbfa2ce2d4526f411338b3b4d01e7e586","tid":56090,"uid":48958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:12:16.000Z","msg":"覺得值唔值得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da62e82de3a4eab602338fc97fd7288604698e60","tid":56090,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:20:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3057e443368155431a15ab5712a3a17fe9f3846","tid":56090,"uid":27564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T15:02:17.000Z","msg":"巴打覺得一個女仔去仰光同蒲廿危唔危險？<br />\n<br />\n果度d人識唔識英文/識幾多？<br />\n<br />\n好想去蒲廿睇佛塔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c39192fe3c724c0dbdd942ed34eb256e59439e2","tid":56090,"uid":13391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T15:51:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我三月去， 果邊會唔會好亂？好似黃警緊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊境打內戰都打咗幾十年<br />\n幾個月前仰光開始有少少亂<br />\n超市有小爆炸 機場有爆炸物 政府辦公室比人炸咗下<br />\n連大金塔都唔比帶水樽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過緬甸警方就話仰光搞事嗰啲就拉咗<br />\n呢個月又真係再聽唔到咩新聞"},{"pid":"08c17ac421922491c1bc7ae5aa327af62978f013","tid":56090,"uid":60315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T01:38:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我下個月都會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問下嗰邊錢面額咁大咁多 你會點袋<br />\n同埋你去係揹backpack定有帶喼<br />\n<br />\n我淨係去仰光蒲甘<br />\n想帶個細喼又怕唔方便</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n美金要用信封或長形銀包裝，唔可以皺<br />\n帶定D 一兩蚊美金，有時用美金抵d<br />\n<br />\nbackpack 去，所以番黎果程要早d 上機，成村人爭飛機上面攞backpack<br />\n<br />\n唔suggest 帶喼去，移動好麻煩，除非你book 晒車玩point to point 接送"},{"pid":"3ca04aa7ae0858aee724e1c2aa072b033d44e5a2","tid":56090,"uid":60315,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T01:41:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>緬甸有咩係必食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RMGmfmSH0MM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRMGmfmSH0MM&d=WUfkuiblbtkL1jM0ISCtEUsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=226686f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RMGmfmSH0MM</a><br />\n<br />\n但衛生情況唔太好，疴左3 次 同嘔左兩次"},{"pid":"cfff42e35ee385f6893226377b85cf8cc4cc85b9","tid":56090,"uid":60315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T01:43:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我三月去， 果邊會唔會好亂？好似黃警緊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n治安完全冇問題，唔好太夜番就得<br />\n但小心唔好北邊邊境，而家打緊仗"},{"pid":"1e208c3ab0d06ffd744e79ac332b7ffbd8d9a8b2","tid":56090,"uid":60315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T01:45:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺得值唔值得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去完會發覺自己世界觀原来咁封閉，佢地英文分分鐘中好過你同我，識得笑鳩强國人冇Facebook 用"},{"pid":"eda5bde065651c22bc8f601dc6901b97f500d4eb","tid":56090,"uid":60315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T01:50:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打覺得一個女仔去仰光同蒲廿危唔危險？<br />\n<br />\n果度d人識唔識英文/識幾多？<br />\n<br />\n好想去蒲廿睇佛塔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇問題的，我係hostel 撞到有個香港女仔都係自己去，但最好路途上搵個伴分擔的士錢<br />\n<br />\n英文方面佢地冇問題，完全可以用英文介紹當地文化同生活，有部分人係華僑，識普通話<br />\n<br />\nbegan 冇去，去得五日"},{"pid":"a22cdcf2b0722e34c079e454e77670b0fa916755","tid":56090,"uid":60315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T01:51:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我三月去， 果邊會唔會好亂？好似黃警緊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊境打內戰都打咗幾十年<br />\n幾個月前仰光開始有少少亂<br />\n超市有小爆炸 機場有爆炸物 政府辦公室比人炸咗下<br />\n連大金塔都唔比帶水樽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過緬甸警方就話仰光搞事嗰啲就拉咗<br />\n呢個月又真係再聽唔到咩新聞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家某D 酒店同景點有行李X光機"},{"pid":"d6f9e70e53698568bc00dac3d9eb7ced367a477b","tid":56090,"uid":27564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-03T17:22:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打覺得一個女仔去仰光同蒲廿危唔危險？<br />\n<br />\n果度d人識唔識英文/識幾多？<br />\n<br />\n好想去蒲廿睇佛塔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇問題的，我係hostel 撞到有個香港女仔都係自己去，但最好路途上搵個伴分擔的士錢<br />\n<br />\n英文方面佢地冇問題，完全可以用英文介紹當地文化同生活，有部分人係華僑，識普通話<br />\n<br />\nbegan 冇去，去得五日</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThx 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n介唔介意透露你去五日洗左幾多錢倒？我聽講緬甸既物價響東南亞國家黎講係數一數二"},{"pid":"199ec049756bf24027a160f6362cd401b82f8bcb","tid":56090,"uid":30528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-03T17:36:36.000Z","msg":"我9月都去左 機票來回$502<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"821d25ab46563e8842f95a3b29f81a588ca0e2db","tid":56090,"uid":69060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-03T17:38:32.000Z","msg":"D水質係咪好差？<br />\n係咪要買水飲？"},{"pid":"65379e4c19142abf4a429427ebc6f9b24a9e1495","tid":56090,"uid":60315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-04T13:50:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打覺得一個女仔去仰光同蒲廿危唔危險？<br />\n<br />\n果度d人識唔識英文/識幾多？<br />\n<br />\n好想去蒲廿睇佛塔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇問題的，我係hostel 撞到有個香港女仔都係自己去，但最好路途上搵個伴分擔的士錢<br />\n<br />\n英文方面佢地冇問題，完全可以用英文介紹當地文化同生活，有部分人係華僑，識普通話<br />\n<br />\nbegan 冇去，去得五日</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThx 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n介唔介意透露你去五日洗左幾多錢倒？我聽講緬甸既物價響東南亞國家黎講係數一數二</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nwithin 4000 all inclusive<br />\n用得最多係的士度，房價聽講係貴過其他國家，但同日韓歐洲比都係勁平"},{"pid":"d2c0bb9fbba6d86b144464c53e90e85ee0abb4b8","tid":56090,"uid":60315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-04T13:53:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>D水質係咪好差？<br />\n係咪要買水飲？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我腸胃差，未試過就咁飲當地水，最多係去超市買當地水飲"},{"pid":"0cd253382e29ee9c9060507d5fbf808de3270d38","tid":56090,"uid":60315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-04T13:54:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我9月都去左 機票來回$502<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nChristmas 來回1200"},{"pid":"f3bfb7c1dfd1d6fd729a52c2e86a5c293a9f38f7","tid":56090,"uid":44323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-11T23:33:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>覺得值唔值得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去完會發覺自己世界觀原来咁封閉，佢地英文分分鐘中好過你同我，識得笑鳩强國人冇Facebook 用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你英文都幾屎"},{"pid":"f4240fc2edf1788520c6fa71bdc33f875992fdab","tid":56090,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-12T00:12:57.000Z","msg":"很好"},{"pid":"eec74d8dc94cc7e1e46e25d87a0320b4560689cf","tid":56090,"uid":63944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-12T00:40:18.000Z","msg":"